There are only a few files here:

users/             A directory containing user logins as YAML
profiles/          A directory of profile page content as YAML

routes.php         The routes in Slim
functions.php      All of the PHP functions - there's really not much here

public/            A folder containing all public assets - this is used as the document root
    index.php
    profile/       A folder for storing image uploads

config/            A folder containing all of the config options - these are just files with values
    theme          An ASCII text file containing the theme name

views/             A folder containing all the templates, namespaced by theme
    <theme_name>/
